 Data Binding Event Binding = Two-Way Binding

  <input type="text" v-model="username">

  v-model is two way data binding for an input.

  when we use it on an input we can get rid of
  -------------------------------------------------------------------
  v-on:input="field_specified"
  v-bind:value="field_specified"
  -------------------------------------------------------------------
  we can easily control the value binding and the input